parent1.code: A sketch of three vibrant, geometric hummingbirds hovering gracefully in the style of abstract cubism. They flutter harmoniously around a crystalline, prismatic flower in a surreal, kaleidoscopic garden on a shimmering summer day, their iridescent wings creating a mesmerizing pattern of light and shadow, with fractured rainbows and swirling, multicolored nectar streams suspended in the air.

offspring.code: A whimsical sketch of three prismatic hummingbirds hovering elegantly in the style of dreamlike abstract cubism. They flutter melodiously around a crystalline flower on a shimmering, ethereal background in a fantastical wonderland on a bright summer day, their wings creating an enchanting display of light, with fractured rainbows and swirling nectar streams suspended in the air.
